---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout title="Privacy Policy">
  <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto p-8">
    <div class="prose prose-lg">
      <h1 class="text-3xl font-bold mb-4">Privacy Policy & Legal Notice</h1>
      <p class="text-blue-600 mb-4">
        Effective Date: January 7, 2025
      </p>
      
      <div class="bg-gray-100 p-4 rounded mb-8">
        <p class="mb-2">
          PLEASE READ THIS PRIVACY POLICY CAREFULLY. THIS POLICY APPLIES TO ALL SERVICES AND WEBSITES OPERATED BY LAKE OZARK CHRISTIAN CHURCH ("THE CHURCH").
        </p>
        <p>
          BY ACCESSING OR USING OUR WEBSITE, YOU ACKNOWLEDGE THAT YOU HAVE READ, UNDERSTOOD, AND AGREE TO BE BOUND BY ALL TERMS OF THIS PRIVACY POLICY AND OUR TERMS OF SERVICE. IF YOU DO NOT AGREE WITH ANY PART OF THIS POLICY, PLEASE DO NOT USE OUR SERVICES.
        </p>
      </div>

      <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold mt-8 mb-4">1. Legal Definitions</h2>
      <p>Throughout this document, the following terms shall have the following meanings:</p>
      <ul class="list-disc pl-5 mb-6">
        <li>"Website" refers specifically to www.lakeozarkdisciples.org and its directly associated subdomains operated by Lake Ozark Christian Church</li>
        <li>"User," "you," or "your" refers to any individual accessing or using the Website</li>
        <li>"We," "us," "our," or "Church" refers to Lake Ozark Christian Church, its employees, officers, and authorized representatives</li>
        <li>"Partners" refers to third-party service providers and organizations with whom we have established formal data processing agreements for website operation and service delivery</li>
      </ul>

      <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold mt-8 mb-4">2. Information Collection and Legal Basis</h2>
      <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold mb-3">2.1 Data Collection Scope</h3>
      <p>We collect and process the following data categories only after obtaining explicit consent or when necessary for our legitimate interests:</p>
      <ul class="list-disc pl-5 mb-6">
        <li>Technical identifiers including IP addresses, cookie data, and browser information - collected only after cookie consent</li>
        <li>Device specifications and settings including operating system, screen configurations, and accessibility preferences - collected for service delivery</li>
        <li>Usage analytics including page views, navigation patterns, and feature interactions - collected with opt-in consent</li>
        <li>Geolocation data (approximate only) for service optimization - collected with explicit permission</li>
      </ul>

      <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold mb-3">2.2 Legal Basis for Processing</h3>
      <p>Our data processing activities are conducted under the following legal bases:</p>
      <ul class="list-disc pl-5 mb-6">
        <li>Legitimate interests in providing and improving our services, which we have documented and balanced against your rights</li>
        <li>Explicit consent obtained through clear affirmative actions (such as clicking "Accept" on our cookie banner or submitting forms)</li>
        <li>Legal obligations and compliance requirements under applicable state, federal, and international laws</li>
      </ul>

      <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold mt-8 mb-4">3. Data Security and Third-Party Processing</h2>
      <p>We implement industry-standard security measures including:</p>
      <ul class="list-disc pl-5 mb-6">
        <li>SSL/TLS encryption for all data transmission</li>
        <li>Regular security audits and penetration testing</li>
        <li>Access controls and authentication requirements</li>
        <li>Data minimization and retention policies</li>
      </ul>
      
      <p>While we do not sell your personal information, we share data with the following categories of processors under strict data processing agreements:</p>
      <ul class="list-disc pl-5 mb-6">
        <li>Website hosting and infrastructure providers</li>
        <li>Analytics services (with anonymization)</li>
        <li>Form processing services</li>
        <li>Security and fraud prevention services</li>
      </ul>

      <p>You can request our current list of processors through our <a href="/report" class="text-blue-600 hover:underline">data subject request form</a>.</p>

      <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold mt-8 mb-4">4. Policy Updates and Changes</h2>
      <p>We may update this policy to reflect changes in our practices or legal requirements. For material changes:</p>
      <ul class="list-disc pl-5 mb-6 bg-yellow-50 p-4 rounded">
        <li>We will provide notice 30 days before changes take effect</li>
        <li>You will receive a cookie consent popup to reconfirm your preferences. </li>
        <li> Your data will be automatically deleted after 30 days if not renewed</li>
        <li>Previous versions will remain accessible in our policy archive</li>
      </ul>

      <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold mt-8 mb-4">5. Your Rights and Choices</h2>
      <p>You have the following rights regarding your personal data:</p>
      <ul class="list-disc pl-5 mb-6">
        <li>Right to access your data (response within 30 days)</li>
        <li>Right to correct inaccurate data (response within 30 days)</li>
        <li>Right to delete your data (response within 30 days)</li>
        <li>Right to withdraw consent at any time</li>
        <li>Right to object to processing based on legitimate interests</li>
      </ul>

      <div class="flex gap-4 my-4">
        <button 
          onclick="window.showCookieSettings()" 
          class="bg-gray-200 px-4 py-2 rounded hover:bg-gray-300"
          aria-label="Open cookie preferences menu"
        >
          Manage Cookie Preferences
        </button>
        <a 
          href="/report" 
          class="bg-blue-600 text-white px-4 py-2 rounded hover:bg-blue-700"
          aria-label="Submit a data subject request"
        >
          Submit Data Subject Request
        </a>
      </div>

      <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold mt-8 mb-4">6. Contact Information</h2>
      <p>For privacy-related inquiries or to exercise your rights:</p>
      <div class="bg-gray-100 p-4 rounded my-4">
        <p>Submit a request through our <a href="/report" class="text-blue-600 hover:underline">data subject request form</a></p>
        <p>Response time: Within 30 days for standard requests</p>
        <p>For urgent matters: <a href="tel:573-365-3366" class="text-blue-600 hover:underline">573-365-3366</a></p>
      </div>

      <hr class="my-8" />

      <div class="text-sm text-gray-600">
        <p>Last Updated: January 7, 2025</p>
        <p>Â© {new Date().getFullYear()} Lake Ozark Christian Church. All rights reserved.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</Layout>
